Package: HOPS
Type: Package
Title: The HOPS (HOrizontal Pleiotropy Score) package allows to compute the Horizontal pleiotropy score as described in Jordan et al. 
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-09-26
Author: Marie Verbanck
Maintainer: <marie.verbanck@mssm.edu>
Description: The HOPS (HOrizontal Pleiotropy Score) package allows to compute the horizontal pleiotropy score as described in Jordan et al. The full set of pleiotropy scores computed on the UK Biobank summary statistics is available through the package using the function RunHOPSApp().
Imports: shiny, shinydashboard, data.table
License: GPL-3
